# HTML5 Canvas

Canvas provides a 2D drawing surface.

## Setup

```html
<canvas id="game" width="800" height="600"></canvas>
```

```javascript
const canvas = document.getElementById('game');
const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
```

## Coordinate System

```
(0,0) ──────> X
  │
  │
  │
  ↓
  Y
```

Top-left is (0,0). X increases right, Y increases down.

## Drawing Primitives

```javascript
// Rectangle
ctx.fillStyle = '#FF0000';
ctx.fillRect(10, 10, 100, 50);

// Circle
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.arc(150, 150, 50, 0, Math.PI * 2);
ctx.fill();

// Line
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.moveTo(0, 0);
ctx.lineTo(100, 100);
ctx.stroke();

// Text
ctx.font = '24px Arial';
ctx.fillText('Hello Game!', 200, 50);
```
